.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-SUBMIT" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.20" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-submit \- Submit a job and optionally watch it
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose submit [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Run the end\-to\-end submission flow: optional preflight, image preparation, script rendering, sbatch submission, and optional live watching of tracked state and logs.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read; if omitted, use the active context compose file or fall back to compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--script\-out\fR \fIOUTPUT\fR
Write the rendered batch script to this path before submission.
.TP
\fB--sbatch\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sbatch executable. Default: sbatch.
.TP
\fB--srun\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the srun executable. Default: srun.
.TP
\fB--enroot\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the enroot executable. Default: enroot.
.TP
\fB--squeue\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the squeue executable. Default: squeue.
.TP
\fB--sacct\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sacct executable. Default: sacct.
.TP
\fB--keep\-failed\-prep\fR
Keep failed preparation state on disk for later inspection.
.TP
\fB--skip\-prepare\fR
Skip image preparation and reuse existing artifacts.
.TP
\fB--force\-rebuild\fR
Refresh imported and prepared artifacts before submission.
.TP
\fB--no\-preflight\fR
Skip the preflight phase before submission.
.TP
\fB--watch\fR
Poll scheduler state and stream tracked logs after submission.
.TP
\fB--dry\-run\fR
Run preflight, prepare, and render without calling sbatch.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose submit \-\-watch \-f compose.yaml
hpc\-compose submit \-\-dry\-run \-f compose.yaml
hpc\-compose submit \-\-skip\-prepare \-f compose.yaml
.fi
